{"tid":1365153,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇電腦高手關於爆ram問題","createTime":"2019-07-25T14:20:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T12:56:02.000Z","uid":119688,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3a241690b3f64c8fffa1f4bf2d1b6d7e17184704","tid":1365153,"uid":119688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T14:20:53.000Z","msg":"呢排唔知咩事 電腦好慢<br />\n我開工作管理員睇到svcost.exe<br />\n爆哂ram打拖慢哂<br />\n上網岩方法整完無用<br />\n得開完機果幾分鐘正常<br />\n電腦一開得耐呢個exe就會自動提高搞到爆ram<br />\n就算我唔開game網頁咩都唔開<br />\n掛係度都會自動爆ram<br />\n求電腦高手解決"},{"pid":"85b8fd3804b6144ab9435b6c4d53d0bc02b10985","tid":1365153,"uid":63452,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T15:37:44.000Z","msg":"唔好上咁多咸網<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">以前部機中過毒又係好多svchost.exe 同爆ram 100% usage，最後洗機了事</span>"},{"pid":"fa4a997cc44d07943fe85d5bfe00df65e5854ff8","tid":1365153,"uid":119688,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"85b8fd3804b6144ab9435b6c4d53d0bc02b10985","tid":1365153,"uid":63452,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T15:37:44.000Z","msg":"唔好上咁多咸網<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">以前部機中過毒又係好多svchost.exe 同爆ram 100% usage，最後洗機了事</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T01:52:37.000Z","msg":"唔想洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a73fdd931296a378e9b0e3e06f2013bab47704c9","tid":1365153,"uid":40684,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T02:19:42.000Z","msg":"唔想洗咪加多條"},{"pid":"010682b737559afb9756ab350fbcb5b4d5ffe017","tid":1365153,"uid":59608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T12:38:45.000Z","msg":"自己攞黎 洗機啦"},{"pid":"98a92ceb98445af2f74fe6524332e8bf3dcae9cc","tid":1365153,"uid":119688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T12:49:01.000Z","msg":"屌 唔想洗"},{"p